</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By James Holston 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
" . . . a valuable contribution to the larger study of modern culture. Its 
merit is to look at the production of modernity as a self-conscious means by 
which people interpret their own history." James Holston 
