determined to get out of the onion fields. ; Photo, 'It's something you look 
forward to. I got an A in everything. . . . It just changed my whole life. 
After I came out, I felt like I could do whatever I wanted.' BRIDGETTE GONZALES 
15-year-old student 
</P>
