<TEXT>
<P>
Your article printed June 17 entitled "Visitors begin to Return to Alaska After 
Spill" was saddening to read. Many tourists who have not ever been to Whittier, 
Alaska, will only have your opinion to rely on. 
</P>
<P>
How sad! 
</P>
