<HEADLINE>
<P>
ERROR ON ART 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In David Nelson's review of La Jolla Seas restaurant ("A Downscale House in an 
Upscale Neighborhood, La Jolla Seas Takes Middle Road," July 13) an error was 
made in the description of the artwork. 
</P>
<P>
Rather than being lithographs, the art, commissioned by Art Consultants-West 
and painted by La Jolla artist Mirto Golino, is original. Each piece was 
created specifically for the La Jolla Seas project. Windansea Beach and La 
Jolla Cove are two local sites depicted in Mirto's original works on paper. 
</P>
<P>
VICTORIA TEAGUE 
</P>
<P>
San Diego 
</P>
