Photo, Celeste Mergens, with son Raymond, makes arrangements for upcoming tax 
protests. At right, she's just a blur at the bottom of the steps, running to 
answer the phone, as her five children play in the living room. BRUCE K. HUFF / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
