<TEXT>
<P>
Los Angeles Superior Court Judge Richard Montes, supervising judge of the 
Family Law Departments, has received an Achievement Award from the National 
Assn. of Counties for changing the court's method of handling divorce cases, 
allowing for quicker resolutions. 
</P>
