how feeling like an immigrant outcast had prompted him to smoke hashish to fit 
in. ; Photo, COLOR, Counselors confront mechanic John Mitchell, left, for not 
making a serious commitment to change. ; Photo, COLOR, Suzan Kidd, right, a 
mother of three young children, chats with a staff member during dinner. ; 
Photo, COLOR, John Mitchell, left, receives a lecture from director Jim 
