<P>
FIGHTING WORDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
U.S. English exists to see that the English language gains official status in 
government -- that no other languages become official. 
</P>
<P>
We are a nation of immigrants with little in common -- not race, religion, 
culture, history. The only thing we have in common is the English language. 
That has been the mortar in the mosaic. 
</P>
<P>
ANGIE PAPADAKIS 
</P>
<P>
Rancho Palos Verdes 
