<TEXT>
<P>
I greatly appreciated your article, "The Grande Dame of Gay Liberation," by 
Bruce Shenitz (June 10). People like Evelyn Hooker should be commended for 
their advocacy on behalf of gays and lesbians -- groups that suffer from 
extreme oppression in our society. We, as a society and as individuals, must 
