NEWPORT BEACH (CA) -- ORDINANCES; FENCES (STRUCTURE) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072990-0208 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 254553 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 29, 1990, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
