<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: ALPHA MICROSYSTEMS NAMES V.P. FOR FINANCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
David A. Young has been named vice president for finance and chief financial 
officer of Alpha Microsystems. 
</P>
<P>
Before joining the Santa Ana computer products company, he was corporate 
controller of California Industrial Products. 
</P>
<P>
Young's previous positions include vice president for finance and 
administration, chief financial officer and secretary and treasurer of San/Bar 
Corp., and vice president of finance and administration, chief financial 
officer and secretary of MSI Data Corp. 
</P>
</TEXT>
